  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    BinaryFunction<L,R,O>, java.util.function.Function<L,O>, Relatable
    Direct Known Subclasses:
    BinaryFunctionChain.LeftFunctionChain, BinaryFunctionChain.RightFunctionChain

    public abstract class BinaryFunctionChain<L,R,V,O>
extends AbstractBinaryFunction<L,R,O>
    Implements a function chain for BinaryFunction instances that will forward an identically typed left or right parameter to the chained function call.
